content:
Leverage Alerts to Evaluate the Quality of Your Predictive Model

Einstein Studio provides alerts to help you manage data discrepancies and issues that can occur during model training. Act on and resolve your alerts to build, retrain, and deploy models that can deliver more accurate predictions. You can review the alerts on the model details page, in model settings, and on the model activity tab.

Where: This change applies to Data Cloud in Developer, Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited editions.

When: This functionality is available starting in July 2024.

title: Evaluating Predictive Model Quality with Einstein Studio
